{"word":"κώδων","slug":"κώδων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n61198\" key=\"kw/dwn\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κώδων</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ωνος</itype><foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">, ὁ</foreign> (<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg003.perseus-grc1:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Aj.\">Aj.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17</biblScope></bibl>, dub. in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg005.perseus-grc1:1078\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pax\">Pax</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1078</biblScope> </bibl>), <sense id=\"n61198.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bell</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὑπ᾽ ἀσπίδος δὲ τῷ χαλκήλατοι κλάζουσι κ. φόνον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg004.perseus-grc1:386\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">386</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg004.perseus-grc1:399\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">399</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg019.perseus-grc1:308\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Rh.\">Rh.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">308</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">χαλκοστόμου κώδωνος ὡς Τυρσηνικῆς</foreign>, i.e. a trumpet, S.l.c. (where Sch. expl. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κώδων</foreign> as <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸ πλατὺ τῆς σάλπιγγος</foreign>, i.e. the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">mouth</tr_> of the trumpet, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0008.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:185a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.185a</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:2:203\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.203</biblScope> </bibl>); carried on rounds of inspection to challenge sentries, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τοῦ κώδωνος πα ενεχθέντος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:135\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.135</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐφοδεύειν κώδωνι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg063:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arat.\">Arat.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg033:24\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Merc.Cond.\">Merc.Cond.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24</biblScope></bibl>, Sch.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg006.perseus-grc1:843\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Av.\">Av.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">843</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n61198.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">crier's bell</tr_>, hence <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ταῦθ᾽ οὗτος μόνον οὐ κώδωνας ἐξαψάμενος διαπράττεται</foreign> 'is his own trumpeter', <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg025.perseus-grc1:90\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">25.90</biblScope> </bibl>: metaph., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἡ κ. ἀκαλανθίς </foreign>(<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὅτι λάλον τὸ ζῷον</foreign> Sch.) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg005.perseus-grc1:1078\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pax\">Pax</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1078</biblScope> </bibl> (perh. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κύων</foreign> is the true reading, <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">App. Prov.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.12</biblScope> </bibl>); cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κρόταλον</foreign>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n61198.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">κωδύα, τῆς μήκωνος</ref> </xr> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Dieuch.</author> </bibl> ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0722.tlg0